column11:
SELECT e.ldoe_dt
INTO   v_ldoe_dt
FROM   employee e
WHERE  e.id = i_entty_uuid

IF v_ldoe_dt IS NULL THEN
	SELECT  it.ldoe_dt
	INTO	v_ldoe_dt
	FROM	inst_term it
			INNER JOIN instruction i
	WHERE	it.inst_uuid = i.id
	AND		it.stts_typ_id NOT IN (CALL GetCmpltSttsTyp)
	AND		i.entty_uuid = i_entty_uuid
END IF
